name: EQ Cleanup
tagline: Cleans up Project EQ so that certain parts are removed
body:
### Who is this for?
If you are working on a custom server using [EQEmulator](http://eqemulator.net) and [Project EQ](http://www.peqtgc.com/), you will know that many changes need to be adjusted in order to make the ideal situation, especially if you plan to make older expansions of Everquest. This contains a collection of scripts with the intention of easing the process of cleaning up the latest PEQ.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with EQ Cleaner? Check out [the forums](http://eqemulator.net) or [create an issue](https://github.com/Xackery/eqcleanup/issues/new) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
